{
  "stem": "985.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Obviously, they needed those furs, the Germans, for their uniforms-- to make uniforms for those who fought on the Russian front.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The winter was coming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was like, I don't know, December, January or so, '42.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, oh, sure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was so frightened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody uttered a word even.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was just a picture of despair on everybody's face.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody was so frightened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were sort of thinking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When they left, and then everybody left unharmed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were four  people-- my father, my mother, my sister and I.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we were thinking, well,  thank God for that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, well, I worked-- worked every day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had various odd jobs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One day there was a strong rain-- there was a small river-- Tysmienica going through the town.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was small.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was, but still was overflowing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we went with the shovels in hands, we had to save whatever we can from the river.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then subsequently, I worked in a big auto repair depot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, in retrospect, the fact that I worked there, and then when we were taken two years later to a different concentration camp in Plaszow I put my occupation as auto mechanic.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that profession next to my name put me eventually on Schindler's list, and I guess, saved my life.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, subsequently, there was a factory-- one day, and it was in 1942, there was so-called action.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was in August '42.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the meantime, the abilities and knowledge of the industry, my father was among very few a handful of men who worked in the office of the headquarters of the petroleum industry [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And command of this whole office was a German by the name of Berthold Beitz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There is a whole story about him I could tell you later maybe.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
